{
  "title": "SentinelLLM Dashboard",
  "description": "Comprehensive monitoring dashboard for LLM observability and security",
  "widgets": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "definition": {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "requests": [
          {
            "q": "avg:sentinel_llm_request_latency{$service}",
            "display_type": "line",
            "style": {
              "palette": "dogmania",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "normal"
            }
          }
        ],
        "title": "LLM Request Latency",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "left",
        "show_legend": true,
        "legend_size": "auto",
        "time": {
          "live_span": "1h"
        },
        "yaxis": {
          "label": "milliseconds",
          "min": "auto",
          "max": "auto"
        }
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 6,
        "height": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "definition": {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "requests": [
          {
            "q": "sum:sentinel_llm_requests{$service}.as_rate()",
            "display_type": "area",
            "style": {
              "palette": "cool",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "normal"
            }
          }
        ],
        "title": "Request Rate",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "left",
        "show_legend": true,
        "legend_size": "auto",
        "time": {
          "live_span": "1h"
        },
        "yaxis": {
          "label": "requests/sec",
          "min": "auto",
          "max": "auto"
        }
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 6,
        "height": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "definition": {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "requests": [
          {
            "q": "sum:sentinel_llm_tokens_input{$service}.as_rate()",
            "display_type": "area",
            "style": {
              "palette": "purple",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "normal"
            }
          },
          {
            "q": "sum:sentinel_llm_tokens_output{$service}.as_rate()",
            "display_type": "area",
            "style": {
              "palette": "green",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "normal"
            }
          }
        ],
        "title": "Token Usage Rate",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "left",
        "show_legend": true,
        "legend_size": "auto",
        "time": {
          "live_span": "1h"
        },
        "yaxis": {
          "label": "tokens/sec",
          "min": "auto",
          "max": "auto"
        }
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "width": 6,
        "height": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "definition": {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "requests": [
          {
            "q": "sum:sentinel_llm_cost_estimate{$service}.as_rate()",
            "display_type": "line",
            "style": {
              "palette": "warm",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "thick"
            }
          }
        ],
        "title": "Cost Rate",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "left",
        "show_legend": true,
        "legend_size": "auto",
        "time": {
          "live_span": "1h"
        },
        "yaxis": {
          "label": "USD/sec",
          "min": "auto",
          "max": "auto"
        }
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 4,
        "width": 6,
        "height": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "definition": {
        "type": "query_value",
        "requests": [
          {
            "q": "avg:sentinel_llm_request_latency{$service}",
            "aggregator": "avg"
          }
        ],
        "title": "Average Latency",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "center",
        "color_preference": "text",
        "custom_unit": "ms",
        "text_align": "center",
        "precision": 2
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8,
        "width": 2,
        "height": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "definition": {
        "type": "query_value",
        "requests": [
          {
            "q": "sum:sentinel_llm_errors{$service}.as_rate()",
            "aggregator": "sum"
          }
        ],
        "title": "Error Rate",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "center",
        "color_preference": "text",
        "custom_unit": "errors/sec",
        "text_align": "center",
        "precision": 2
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 2,
        "y": 8,
        "width": 2,
        "height": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "definition": {
        "type": "query_value",
        "requests": [
          {
            "q": "sum:sentinel_llm_prompt_injection_detected{$service}.as_rate()",
            "aggregator": "sum"
          }
        ],
        "title": "Security Violations",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "center",
        "color_preference": "text",
        "custom_unit": "violations/sec",
        "text_align": "center",
        "precision": 2
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 4,
        "y": 8,
        "width": 2,
        "height": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "definition": {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "requests": [
          {
            "q": "sum:sentinel_llm_requests{$service}",
            "display_type": "count",
            "style": {
              "palette": "blue",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "normal"
            }
          }
        ],
        "title": "Total Requests",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "left",
        "show_legend": false,
        "time": {
          "live_span": "1h"
        }
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 8,
        "width": 6,
        "height": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "# SentinelLLM Observability Dashboard\n\nThis dashboard provides comprehensive monitoring for:\n\n- **Performance**: Request latency and throughput\n- **Security**: Prompt injection detection and violations\n- **Cost**: Token usage and cost tracking\n- **Reliability**: Error rates and system health\n\nConfigure alerts for critical metrics using the monitors in this dashboard.",
        "background_color": "blue",
        "font_size": "14",
        "text_align": "left",
        "show_tick": false,
        "tick_pos": "50%",
        "tick_edge": "left"
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 10,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 3
      }
    }
  ],
  "layout_type": "ordered",
  "is_read_only": false,
  "notify_list": [],
  "template_variables": [
    {
      "name": "service",
      "default": "*",
      "prefix": "service",
      "available_values": []
    }
  ],
  "template_variable_uses": [
    {
      "name": "service",
      "filters": [
        {
          "name": "service",
          "value": "$service"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

